{"id":9729,"date":"2012-11-09T22:02:25","date_gmt":"2012-11-10T03:02:25","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=9729"},"modified":"2023-06-06T18:28:13","modified_gmt":"2023-06-06T14:28:13","slug":"no-omens-women","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/09\/no-omens-women\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Superstition: No omens in women, houses, or animals"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Hassan al-A\u2019raj reported: Two men entered the home of Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, and they said, \u201cAbu Huraira narrates that the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said: Verily, omens are in women, animals, and houses.\u201d Aisha became upset and she said, \u201cBy the one who revealed the Quran to Abu al-Qasim, it is not like that. The\u00a0Prophet was saying: <strong>The people of ignorance used to say omens are in women, houses, and animals<\/strong>.\u201d Then, she recited the verse, \u201c<strong>No affliction occurs in the earth or within yourselves except that it is written in a book.<\/strong>\u201d (57:22)<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 26088<\/p>\n<p>Grade:<strong> <em>Sahih\u00a0<\/em><\/strong>(authentic) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0631\u064e\u062c\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062f\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0627 \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u064a\u064f\u062d\u064e