ou hears.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5754, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2223 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19271,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/03\/following-omen-shirk\/","url_meta":{"origin":9729,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Omens: Following omens an act of idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever turns back from something due to seeing an omen, he has committed idolatry.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the expiation for that?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat he says: O Allah, there\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/16\/prophet-optimistic-good-expectations\/","url_meta":{"origin":9729,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Optimism: The Prophet was optimistic, had good expectations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was optimistic, he did not see evil omens, and he liked good names. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2762 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\